OL,3,CThe hidden health costs of wood-
OL,4,Cburning stoves and open fires
OL,6,F"There is no safe level of air
OL,7,Fpollution," says the report.
OL,9,F"Fine particulate matter released
OL,10,Fduring combustion has the ability to
OL,11,Fpenetrate deep into the lungs and
OL,12,Fbloodstream, affecting every organ in
OL,13,Fthe body, and leading to or
OL,14,Fexacerbating various health issues."
OL,16,FThis can cause heart and lung disease,
OL,17,Fas well as contribute to new cases of
OL,18,Fserious health conditions.
