OL,3,CThe hidden health costs of wood-
OL,4,Cburning stoves and open fires
OL,6,F"For children with asthma, even small
OL,7,Fincreases in indoor air pollution can
OL,8,Fmean more frequent flare-ups, hospital
OL,9,Fadmissions, and time away from school
OL,10,F` consequences that are entirely
OL,11,Fpreventable with cleaner heating
OL,12,Fchoices.
OL,14,F"It's not just our own homes that will
OL,15,Fbe impacted, but the air that makes it
OL,16,Finto the homes of our neighbours as
OL,17,Fwell."
